the same impulses.

1530
01:26:32,145 --> 01:26:33,688
Don't jump to conclusions
about that impulse.

1531
01:26:33,856 --> 01:26:35,189
That impulse is
a good impulse, Julie.

1532
01:26:35,440 --> 01:26:37,108
