Wait a second.

1543
01:26:57,170 --> 01:26:58,713
Dorothy, you've got to see him.

1544
01:26:58,881 --> 01:27:01,340
I don't care what you tell him,
just don't lead him on.

1545
01:27:01,508 --> 01:27:04,552
