1553
01:27:30,370 --> 01:27:32,079
Scotch and bourbon.

1554
01:27:33,498 --> 01:27:34,582
I'd like to...

1555
01:27:34,791 --> 01:27:36,375
Let's dance.
What?

1556
01:27:36,627 --> 01:27:39,587
It's my favourite dance.
Oh, really, I don't dance.

1557
01:27:40,088 --> 01:27:41,172
You'll love it.
