1568
01:28:20,128 --> 01:28:22,338
I was real happy when you
could come out tonight.

1569
01:28:22,589 --> 01:28:25,257
I know you usually
got a lot of lines to learn.

1570
01:28:25,550 --> 01:28:27,551
Les, I think there's
something I'd better say.

1571
01:28:27,719 --> 01:28:29,220
